I"u<p>The manuscript <strong>Evolution of warfare by resource raiding favors polymorphism in belligerence and bravery</strong>, by professors C. Mullon and L. Lehmann, was recently accepted in <em>Philosophical Transactions of the Royal Society B</em>. The preprint is already available <a href="https://www.biorxiv.org/content/10.1101/2021.11.01.466436v1">at BioXiv</a>.</p>
